# Project-level ShellCheck config for sourced Bash modules.
# Keep this file in sync with CI and VS Code shellcheck.customArgs.
#
# SC1091 (not following sourced files) is suppressed via --exclude on the
# command line because the snap shellcheck ignores 'disable=' in rc files.
# All modules and profiles are sourced dynamically at runtime, so static
# source following is intentionally not supported.

source-path=SCRIPTDIR
source-path=.
severity=info
